<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#b7709e4044df5d7d33ca8f7460b06f8f>.
<#b7709e4044df5d7d33ca8f7460b06f8f> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://opendata-catalog.smhi.se/md/0757b95c-829b-43da-8864-6cee947c93ce>;
