<https://opendata-catalog.smhi.se/md/9d8a1894-9f6c-4d74-9d2e-d481f8737ced> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/spatial> _:b0__73750.
_:b0__73750 <http://www.w3.org/ns/locn#geometry> "POLYGON((-15.32 71.91,49.61 71.91,49.61 51.47,-15.32 51.47,-15.32 71.91))"^^<http://www.opengis.net/ont/geosparql#wktLiteral>;
