<https://opendata-catalog.smhi.se/md/9d8a1894-9f6c-4d74-9d2e-d481f8737ced> <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#contactPoint> <https://www.smhi.se/data/utforskaren-oppna-data/kundtjanst_smhi.se>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#distribution> <https://opendata-download-grid-archive.smhi.se/feed/5>, <https://opendata-view.smhi.se/grid-archive/arome_extent/wms?service=wms&request=getcapabilities>, <https://opendata.smhi.se/gridarchive/index_met>, <https://www.smhi.se/data/temperatur-och-vind/temperatur/historisk-data-i-grib-format/sa-fungerar-grib-format>, <https://www.smhi.se/data/temperatur-och-vind/temperatur/historisk-data-i-grib-format/arome>, <urn:uuid:e0c57e61-41bb-c47b-6748-f5a220b517db>, <urn:uuid:7a82d1d4-0157-9048-cad7-35d3bff0eda3>, <urn:uuid:e9e5e835-6fa8-b305-4987-c86bb0272bdd>, <urn:uuid:636a3f53-f054-543d-0f52-66e56b2d0ae2>, <urn:uuid:67553301-1b76-dbb3-e6a0-5dd5371c77b0>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/issued> "2014-03-20"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#date>;
    <http://data.europa.eu/r5r/applicableLegislation> <http://data.europa.eu/eli/reg_impl/2023/138/oj>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/modified> "2024-05-03"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#date>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/title> "Meteorologisk prognosmodell (AROME) - historiska analysdata"@sv;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#theme> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/data-theme/ENVI>, <http://inspire.ec.europa.eu/theme/mf>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#dataQuality> "Prognosmodellen använder fysikaliska lagar, t ex rörelseekvationer, termodynamiska samband, strålnings- och kontinuitetsekvationer för att beräkna vädrets förändring i ett antal tidssteg framåt i tiden.";
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/conformsTo> <http://www.w3.org/TR/vocab-dcat/>;
