}

<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#83cbb4294749c39eb87c15c30a68ca6c>.
<#83cbb4294749c39eb87c15c30a68ca6c> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://opendata-catalog.smhi.se/md/a47932fd-8b6a-47cd-a8e7-429f3c750bdc>;
