    a <http://purl.org/dc/terms/Location>.
<https://opendata-catalog.smhi.se/md/cb15b040-32bf-11ea-91f2-0b81cad13edd> <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#contactPoint> <https://www.smhi.se/data/utforskaren-oppna-data/klimatolog_smhi.se>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#distribution> <https://opendata.smhi.se/metobs/api>, <https://www.smhi.se/data/hitta-data-for-en-plats/ladda-ner-vaderobservationer/snowDepth>, <https://opendata-download-metobs.smhi.se/api/version/latest/parameter/40.json>, <urn:uuid:4b6c0f85-0482-f539-5f96-ac6e243e5b6a>, <urn:uuid:9d49c454-4f93-f84c-c2bc-460bc2a77056>, <urn:uuid:6c727420-716f-4a56-195c-7badabd7b725>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/issued> "2020-01-09"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#date>;
