<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#98a5c5f5fb5ec0cbb2ae01d9c9f32d75>.
<#98a5c5f5fb5ec0cbb2ae01d9c9f32d75> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
