<https://opendata-catalog.smhi.se/md/c9e0e8f2-bdab-4d86-b84e-9c05051e152d> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/spatial> _:b0__54619.
_:b0__54619 <http://www.w3.org/ns/locn#geometry> "POLYGON((9.32 69.42,29.80 69.42,29.80 53.87,9.32 53.87,9.32 69.42))"^^<http://www.opengis.net/ont/geosparql#wktLiteral>;
