<http://data.naturvardsverket.se/resources/993a7ed2-4e69-47e8-ae01-ed3ab64aae5d> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/accrualPeriodicity> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/frequency/UNKNOWN>;
