    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#published> "2026-03-27T06:27:21.059Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>.
<#078fd5fd036c8c110b513e69cc652d86> {
<https://catalog.skara.se/store/1/resource/95> <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#downloadURL> <https://catalog.skara.se/store/1/resource/94>;
