    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://ckan-malmo.dataplatform.se/dataset/3c36006c-8fc8-46ab-8862-7b5051347e6c/resource/a80d50b4-67ac-455b-a2c3-d3409445a417>;
